[img]http://i173.photobucket.com/albums/w48/sigmaker222/Rs2NetworkBanner.jpg[/img] ---Please Visit Site To Get Involved!!!----- [url=http://www.rs2network.co.nr]www.rs2network.co.nr[/url]
If you are good with webclient's, pm me please. I'm making my server need a webclient to play. So people won't use cheat client's, etc.
This is the newest server i'm making. It will be based in FULLY REAL RUNESCAPE,
I have switched to a more stable and reliable server.
---Please Visit Site To Get Involved!!!----- [url=http://www.rs2network.co.nr]www.rs2network.co.nr[/url]
IRC :
the chat room is on the site its on the index section (forum area) you will have to register to chat on it.
Goals :
-Rent a dedicated -Fix up forums -Get a runescape kind of site -fix errors and accomplish 459 terrain
Accomplished: -Perfect Teleporting. -No more Azn Client crashing. bitchs Tongue. -fully working runescape everything (apart from guide person) -working varrock fountain (459) -71% home port =)
Well, I am going to spend some money and alot of time into this. Once i'm done with the server, I am going to buy a domain, then make a site with some help.
WHAT I NEED (jobs avalible)
Client Coders::
Matrx -open -open -open
Webclient Coders::
Matrx -open -open
Note:: please note that if you help out you may be rewarded as a admin or a mod. we will also give you runescape items , accs and more!!!!!!!!
=> Please Visit The Site To Get Involved In A Better Way Instead Posting Here. But If You Dont Have Time You Can Always Post Here.
